---

<section class="community reveal" id="community">
  <div class="community-container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">/community</h2>
    <p class="community-headline">Build with AI. Together.</p>
    <p class="community-text">
      Join Frinter Core — a community for builders creating real products with AI.
      Share what you're building, get help, and connect with others who moved past tutorials.
    </p>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/sUq42Mcah6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="community-cta">
      Join Frinter Core on Discord ↗
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .community {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-elevated);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--violet);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--violet);
  }
  .community-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .community-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .community-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .community-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--violet);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--violet);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .community-cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--violet);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--violet-glow);
  }
</style>
